[7.034144, "o", "# ship-log brief\r\n_focus: src/store.py В· 1 dead-end В· 3 of 3 entries_\r\n\r\n## Dead-ends (do NOT redo)\r\n- `260625-PQ4FWF` Threaded the append path; lock contention made it slower вҖ” GIL + fsync per write _(src/store.py)_\r\n\r\n## Decisions\r\n- `260625-CM4XME` Use JSONL not SQLite for the store вҖ” merge-friendly + greppable _(src/store.py)_\r\n\r\n## Recent (attempts / notes)\r\n- `260625-F610K6` Config lives in .shiplog/config.toml\r\n"]
